| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1465 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: f869f4e2-ab6e-532b-98fc-aad15c6ecbc7"
